.el .ds Aq '
.TH antimony 1  "antimony 5.2.1" 
.SH NAME
antimony \- Sandbox Applications
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBantimony\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sandbox Applications
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
antimony\-run(1)
Run a profile
.TP
antimony\-edit(1)
Edit an existing profile
.TP
antimony\-refresh(1)
Refresh caches
.TP
antimony\-integrate(1)
Integrate a profile into the user environment
.TP
antimony\-remove(1)
Remove features/profiles, or reset user definitions to the default
.TP
antimony\-export(1)
Export user profiles
.TP
antimony\-import(1)
Import user profiles
.TP
antimony\-info(1)
Get information about profiles/features
.TP
antimony\-package(1)
Package a profile into a self\-contained executable
.TP
antimony\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH VERSION
v5.2.1
